@startuml Artifact Lineage Overview
title Artifact Lineage Overview

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

artifact raw_data_snapshot as "Raw Data Snapshot"
artifact interim_dataset_snapshot as "Interim Dataset Snapshot"
artifact processed_dataset_snapshot as "Processed Dataset Snapshot"
artifact feature_set_snapshot as "Feature Set Snapshot"
artifact search_run_snapshot as "Search Run Snapshot"
artifact train_run_snapshot as "Train Run Snapshot"
artifact evaluation_run_snapshot as "Evaluation Run Snapshot"
artifact explainability_run_snapshot as "Explainability Run Snapshot"
artifact promotion_run_snapshot as "Promotion Run Snapshot"

raw_data_snapshot --> interim_dataset_snapshot
interim_dataset_snapshot --> processed_dataset_snapshot
processed_dataset_snapshot --> feature_set_snapshot

feature_set_snapshot --> search_run_snapshot
note right of feature_set_snapshot
Input and derived schemas are stored at
the version level (same across all snapshots)
end note

search_run_snapshot --> train_run_snapshot
train_run_snapshot --> evaluation_run_snapshot
train_run_snapshot --> explainability_run_snapshot

evaluation_run_snapshot --> promotion_run_snapshot
explainability_run_snapshot --> promotion_run_snapshot

legend right
-->   Artifact lineage / flow
endlegend

@enduml